{"tid":2079226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有手足講槍啦 槍真係個個都應該有","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T15:51:36.000Z","uid":347987,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf8e295bfcbcd5243b02a0206b4e24fa7728287","tid":2079226,"uid":347987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZYgEZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZYgEZC.jpg&h=1525e9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#思想解放 #還權於民 【止戈為武，舉槍制暴】<br />\n<br />\n當太平盛世時，我們不需庸人自擾，思索如何自衛。但當法制崩潰時，就必須懂得保護自己，而「槍權」就是人民的法槌。<br />\n<br />\n《美國憲法第二修正案》確立了人民持槍的權利。雖香港不像美國，沒有野獸的威脅，但在警黑勾結、無法無天的環境下，香港人其實正面對更大的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n法律允許警察持有槍械、行使武力，是便於他們執法，使罪犯屈服於恐懼武力的人性。但當警權失控、法治崩潰，人民便有權運用持槍權，以武力提點失控的人回歸理性，以合法槍權威懾失控極權。在這個時候，人民手中的槍，才是捍衛民權的最後防線。<br />\n<br />\n對等武力，互保平安。<br />\n<br />\n現正招募義工🙏🏻 ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdzWunQYVLwybej4p5OMqpzW_y8b8QXycVgj8Ytzt-BQ9QvWw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdzWunQYVLwybej4p5OMqpzW_y8b8QXycVgj8Ytzt-BQ9QvWw%2Fviewform&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SoD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=4d0d3def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdzWunQYVLwybej4p5OMqpzW_y8b8QXycVgj8Ytzt-BQ9QvWw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港人日程表 #光復香港 #反國安法<br />\n＿＿＿＿＿＿＿<br />\n#劉澤鋒 <br />\n<br />\n-Instagram&bull; Nathanlau612<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/nathanlau612?igshid=69lzavz7f9o3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fnathanlau612%3Figshid%3D69lzavz7f9o3&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SoD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=37d13213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/nathanlau612?igshid=69lzavz7f9o3</a><br />\n-Facebook &bull; 劉澤鋒 Nathan Lau<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Nathanlau612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FNathanlau612&d=b6PV2mH